12 June 2017The African National Congress (ANC) sends its heartfelt condolences to member of the ANC National Executive Committee and South African Communist Party (SACP) General Secretary Comrade Blade Nzimande and his family on the passing of his mother, Mama Nozipho Nzimande. Mama Nzimande passed on Sunday evening at the age of 90 years.May the Nzimande family find peace and comfort during this difficult time in the long full life lived by their mother and memories of the time they spent together. It is said that when the time one shared with a loved person becomes a memory, that memory becomes a treasure.May her soul rest in everlasting peace.Issued by the African National CongressEnquiries Zizi Kodwa 082 330 4910 National Spokesperson Khusela Sangoni 072 854 5707 National Communications Manager